Local Arrangements:
All workshop participants including the presenters will be required =20
to register for ESSLLI. The registration fee for authors presenting a =20=

paper will correspond to the early student/workshop speaker =20
registration fee. Moreover, a number of additional fee waiver grants =20
will be made available by the OC on a competitive basis and workshop =20
participants are eligible to apply for those.

There will be no reimbursement for travel costs and accommodation. =20
Workshop speakers who have difficulty in finding funding should =20
contact the local organizing committee to ask for the possibilities =20
for a grant.

